modName: A Cute Redguard Cat - lvl 1 save game
summary:
She is a cat. You will love her, she may like you back. 

Download meow.
descriptionHtml:
In a world of plastic barbie clones
In a land of lightnings
From a dream that I would never share with relatives
From the creator of The Sir

A Cute Redguard Cat. Lilla.


After my PM box was literally inundated with a message requesting her, I was compelled to share. Don\'t just download and stick her in a dark collection folder like some perverted freak! She\'s a cat, play with her. Purr, purr.



- V1 at helgen keep level 0/1 (pics in white armor)
- V2 level 5, slightly tweaked face and skin. carryweight cheat. (cat and short hair close ups) 

Download, endorse and/or leave a comment and I may send you a pizza or tootsie roll.



* mods to look like pics/suggested:

Coverwomen look 2 without brows (and with optional lace tattoos for V2)
Natural eyes
Straight hair retexture (by navetsea)
CBBE slim
White armor is eisen platte
White and gold armor is Dynasty/Ironmaiden armor 
Optional Dynasty textures can be found on Oblivion Nexus 
Cat ears is a wig from meng/ebony samurai armor
Green and gold armor is meng/ebony samurai armor

dj kindly posted links and info on armors in comments section

New pics have:
Kaw Cat Disguise: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=6150&navtag=file/images.php?id=6150&tab=3
Striped Underwear retex: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=6149
My type of hair (long hair): http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=6173

A special thanks to all the modders that bring us closer to a CatRim :)
